{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory registration and licensing for e-bikes.",
        "additional_details": "We believe a registration system helps to decrease the risk of individuals purchasing second-hand e-bikes that may be defective or unlawfully modified. Requiring e-bike riders to have a license could aid in preventing underage riders through the enforcement of stricter identification protocols. Licensing also ensures that riders possess the necessary experience and are familiar with road regulations.",
        "background": "We want the government to introduce mandatory registration and licensing alongside other regulations to align the system with what is in place for mopeds.",
